graph TB
    subgraph "RHODS Operator Component"
        DSCController[DataScienceCluster Controller]
        DSCIController[DSCInitialization Controller]
        SecretGen[SecretGenerator Controller]
        CertGen[CertConfigmapGenerator Controller]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        ManifestFetcher[Manifest Fetcher]

        subgraph "Component Reconcilers"
            Dashboard[Dashboard Reconciler]
            KServe[KServe Reconciler]
            ModelMesh[ModelMesh Reconciler]
            DSP[Data Science Pipelines Reconciler]
            Workbenches[Workbenches Reconciler]
            CodeFlare[CodeFlare Reconciler]
            Ray[Ray Reconciler]
            Kueue[Kueue Reconciler]
            Training[Training Operator Reconciler]
            TrustyAI[TrustyAI Reconciler]
        end

        DSCController -->|uses| ManifestFetcher
        DSCController -->|orchestrates| Dashboard
        DSCController -->|orchestrates| KServe
        DSCController -->|orchestrates| ModelMesh
        DSCController -->|orchestrates| DSP
        DSCController -->|orchestrates| Workbenches
        DSCController -->|orchestrates| CodeFlare
        DSCController -->|orchestrates| Ray
        DSCController -->|orchestrates| Kueue
        DSCController -->|orchestrates| Training
        DSCController -->|orchestrates| TrustyAI
        DSCIController -->|generates| SecretGen
        DSCIController -->|generates| CertGen
    end

    User[User/Admin] -->|creates| DSCCR[DataScienceCluster CR]
    User -->|creates| DSCICR[DSCInitialization CR]

    DSCCR -->|validates/mutates| Webhook
    DSCICR -->|validates/mutates| Webhook

    Webhook -->|validated| DSCController
    Webhook -->|validated| DSCIController

    ManifestFetcher -->|fetches from| GitHub[GitHub Repositories<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]

    DSCController -->|creates| FeatureTracker[FeatureTracker CRs]
    DSCController -->|creates| ComponentResources[Component Resources]

    DSCIController -->|creates| Namespaces[Managed Namespaces]
    DSCIController -->|configures| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh Config]
    DSCIController -->|deploys| Monitoring[Monitoring Stack]

    SecretGen -->|creates| Secrets[Component Secrets]
    CertGen -->|creates| CACerts[CA Certificate ConfigMaps]

    %% External dependencies
    DSCController -->|depends on| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    ServiceMesh -->|integrates| Istio[Service Mesh Operator]
    KServe -->|requires| Knative[Knative Serving]

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes| Metrics[Metrics Endpoint<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]

    style DSCController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style DSCIController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style DSCCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style DSCICR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style FeatureTracker fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style GitHub fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Istio fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Knative fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
